like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:14:13.000Z","msg":"點解五官會出現西同波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:27:46.000Z","msg":"波囉腋西腳<br />\n五官"},{"pid":"e364aebc266ff0732969eda5807aba9585029a24","tid":2360010,"uid":42213,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"b24746ad752e5cb265874f41042f5fc4aed76996","tid":2360010,"uid":343229,"like":15,"dislike":18,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"e69f4fc0d862fd0ddad538207f150b7443303a51","tid":2360010,"uid":262737,"like":225,"dislike":1,"score":224,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T11:32:08.000Z","msg":"唔記得邊位巴打講過<br />\n眼決定上限<br />\n鼻口決定下限<br />\n<br />\n眼唔靚，靚極有限<br />\n鼻口靚，醜極有限<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得好準"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T12:12:58.000Z","msg":"調轉左下話？<br />\n眼係下限 鼻係上限<br />\n眼靚既柒極有限<br />\n但鼻靚先做到靚人<br />\n不過最尾都係睇整體<br />\n輪廓、五官、皮膚、氣質、三庭五眼樣樣都緊要<br />\n見過唔少眼同鼻都唔差既個樣都炒晒車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:34:02.000Z","msg":"唔係啦<br />\n大把人就算眼好靚 但鼻嘴唔靚真係柒到無得救<br />\n但鼻口靚 眼柒 你第一印象都會覺得係靚<br />\n好似余德丞咁 隻眼柒到咁 都大把人覺得係靚仔"},{"pid":"8c865d82340b8f24e2a6edd7ca0e4bacd2007c10","tid":2360010,"uid":228909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"499a465a3ba04be1cbc231704efe744411c0e44c","tid":2360010,"uid":162930,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T11:31:16.000Z","msg":"鼻，眼有得化同痴膠紙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:35:37.000Z","msg":"所有都有得化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b3ebe90350b6ca9a23df4a35f70aea1f9462a4","tid":2360010,"uid":102783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eb35b1aac4c3df9b9936eef60a2cb7167a25c062","tid":2360010,"uid":203543,"like":4,"dislike":24,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"f21d33227b6b06cce0a973ea8d54e65f3ab6c46f","tid":2360010,"uid":5591,"like":6,"dislike":12,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T11:11:13.000Z","msg":"對波"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T11:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PhCmyF5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPhCmyF5.jpg&h=9001418f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:40:03.000Z","msg":"又嚇人 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b64ecb89d2f6a1a7a6b2e954787f12f93cba6d","tid":2360010,"uid":96218,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:43:55.000Z","msg":"嘴 單眼皮同鳳眼都各有各靚 但係哨牙/嘴突/下巴後縮真係對眼幾靚都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb27132e9e57a849eb3bfc14d0fc9dcbbe6ee51","tid":2360010,"uid":212336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:50:51.000Z","msg":"眼耳口鼻最多咪得耳係次要啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23858894738ed96c3ca7d9e8ca9cbc1ecdfce03","tid":2360010,"uid":96218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f00c23d28356119ed9dd629b73959d535e79e436","tid":2360010,"uid":236422,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T13:45:29.000Z","msg":"西方人輪廓配東方人五官 我覺得係最靚最完美<br />\n輪廓五官比例最緊要 最好係1:1:1 三庭五眼無得輸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90050c13b0aad9a7dc1e216f86e7086b52aea31b","tid":2360010,"uid":379493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01b64ecb89d2f6a1a7a6b2e954787f12f93cba6d","tid":2360010,"uid":96218,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:43:55.000Z","msg":"嘴 單眼皮同鳳眼都各有各靚 但係哨牙/嘴突/下巴後縮真係對眼幾靚都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:51:38.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n同唔識合口"},{"pid":"e42bb69802e6dbbd658aa0ac96c4c35d1250dd95","tid":2360010,"uid":314825,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:53:12.000Z","msg":"鼻<br />\n其他五官點樣衰都好，個鼻好睇都會好有氣質，同埋其他五官可以靠化妝救，鼻呢d 咁立體嘅野剩係靠修容救唔到幾多"},{"pid":"3b58a1e3f755bf12d83ace4297b45f552fbbc535","tid":2360010,"uid":314825,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"c22a6458ce9e55aea0c535ed2e7d44603e39914a","tid":2360010,"uid":368023,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T13:29:34.000Z","msg":"覺得係面型<br />\n單眼皮可以癡膠紙/用膠水<br />\n鼻可以打鼻影<br />\n但面型就算打咗陰影，差別都係好細<br />\n面大嘅人好睇嘅髮型好有限<br />\n同面細嘅人比，影相望落唔精緻/好大咪/比例差"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:58:16.000Z","msg":"但係其實鼻影救唔到幾多，始終鼻係五官入面最立體嘅野，你個鼻影打得幾靚都好，一睇側面就出曬事"},{"pid":"9f71f17fa5f9258d239d73791b6c93f2e177dbde","tid":2360010,"uid":293522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:10:42.000Z","msg":"認同鼻最緊要。<br />\n眼口唔係標準靚拼埋都可以有吸引力，<br />\n但鼻唔靚就點都怪。e.g. 周秀娜、阿蛇"},{"pid":"32ba916010109f75e8b910ca9dff0435deb4e60c","tid":2360010,"uid":92442,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:16:51.000Z","msg":"鼻同嘴打和"},{"pid":"48b3bf6064b681858a6d560edfcc89756f74559b","tid":2360010,"uid":364468,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:23:06.000Z","msg":"一定係鼻<br />\n<br />\n我本身都真係ok 靚仔 乾淨 陽光<br />\n但個鼻係闊左少少 最慘唔太高<br />\n有時影相都差啲<br />\n搞到有時冇乜自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好想去打高少少個鼻 先可以有新既突破<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eccaf16d889b31b4c3e42456bd455893458b696e","tid":2360010,"uid":96218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90050c13b0aad9a7dc1e216f86e7086b52aea31b","tid":2360010,"uid":379493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01b64ecb89d2f6a1a7a6b2e954787f12f93cba6d","tid":2360010,"uid":96218,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:43:55.000Z","msg":"嘴 單眼皮同鳳眼都各有各靚 但係哨牙/嘴突/下巴後縮真係對眼幾靚都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:51:38.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n同唔識合口"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:34:29.000Z","msg":"岩呀 之前見過ig有個韓國女仔對眼好靚 但係棚牙西瓜刨咁 教化妝搽唇膏係突棚牙出嚟搽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似形住佢擘大口呼吸個口好臭咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過牙柒好處係箍牙冇人會當係整容 反而你眼柒去割雙眼皮就個個都認同你整左容"},{"pid":"69c101981e1de55fbe1908153381878acac125ec","tid":2360010,"uid":236422,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:39:57.000Z","msg":"單眼皮靚過外雙（男）當年內雙係最好"},{"pid":"b183bb5101ccd00f1f6578dcac5b3595e0cfd282","tid":2360010,"uid":349947,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:43:24.000Z","msg":"絕對係眼 就算望 第一眼都係望眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cb9d81740443a2836f3d734dd688aef153fd0c","tid":2360010,"uid":321262,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:44:29.000Z","msg":"眼喇，見過鼻加嘴柒嘅靠眼去頂，如果眼差d，就要鼻加嘴好先夠頂到，換言之，眼可以補救2樣嘢，如果眼差的話，要2樣嘢好先補救到，試下眼差，鼻好，嘴差，一樣都係柒"},{"pid":"a14bb87f811c76735d6b1d808a428d5f4b1f0e45","tid":2360010,"uid":236422,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"59cb9d81740443a2836f3d734dd688aef153fd0c","tid":2360010,"uid":321262,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:44:29.000Z","msg":"眼喇，見過鼻加嘴柒嘅靠眼去頂，如果眼差d，就要鼻加嘴好先夠頂到，換言之，眼可以補救2樣嘢，如果眼差的話，要2樣嘢好先補救到，試下眼差，鼻好，嘴差，一樣都係柒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:45:46.000Z","msg":"男鼻柒 眼點靚都救唔到"},{"pid":"77b6b311f4c892f67d90072f9572cc70c00dd3cd","tid":2360010,"uid":321262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a14bb87f811c76735d6b1d808a428d5f4b1f0e45","tid":2360010,"uid":236422,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"59cb9d81740443a2836f3d734dd688aef153fd0c","tid":2360010,"uid":321262,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:44:29.000Z","msg":"眼喇，見過鼻加嘴柒嘅靠眼去頂，如果眼差d，就要鼻加嘴好先夠頂到，換言之，眼可以補救2樣嘢，如果眼差的話，要2樣嘢好先補救到，試下眼差，鼻好，嘴差，一樣都係柒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:45:46.000Z","msg":"男鼻柒 眼點靚都救唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:48:38.000Z","msg":"未必，可能接觸到嘅其實係鼻柒眼都柒埋嗰